<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Healthcare Cost Estimator</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <header class="app-header navbar bg-white shadow-sm border-bottom py-3">
        <div class="container-fluid px-4">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold text-dark fs-4" href="#">BrandLogo</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="app-wrapper position-relative bg-light d-flex flex-column">
        
        <div id="hero-animations" class="shape-container z-1">
            <div class="welcome-blue-gradient"></div>
            <div class="half-donut-fixed welcome-donut"></div>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1538356111053-748a48e1acb8?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&h=250&q=80" id="welcome-footer-img" alt="Footer" class="hero-image shadow-lg">
        </div>

        <div id="spiral-container" class="bottom-right-arcs z-1">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 500 500" class="w-100 h-100">
                <path d="M 20 500 A 480 480 0 0 1 500 20" class="draw-arc" pathLength="100" />
                <path d="M 80 500 A 420 420 0 0 1 500 80" class="draw-arc" pathLength="100" />
                <path d="M 140 500 A 360 360 0 0 1 500 140" class="draw-arc" pathLength="100" />
                <path d="M 200 500 A 300 300 0 0 1 500 200" class="draw-arc" pathLength="100" />
                <path d="M 260 500 A 240 240 0 0 1 500 260" class="draw-arc" pathLength="100" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-grow-1 position-relative z-2">
            
            <div id="onboarding-flow-container" class="content-offset pt-5">
                
                <div id="progress-container" class="transition-opacity opacity-0 mb-5 custom-progress-width">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mb-2">
                        <span id="progress-text" class="text-dark fw-bold fs-6">0 out of 12 questions answered</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="progress" style="height: 14px; border-radius: 8px;">
                        <div id="app-progress" class="progress-bar custom-theme-bar transition-width" role="progressbar" style="width: 0%;"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <section class="step-panel panel welcome-layout">
                    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3 text-dark">Plan today. Retire with more confidence</h1>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-4 fs-4" style="line-height: 1.6; max-width: 900px;">Learn how informed health care choices can enhance your retirement security. By answering a few questions, we can provide a personalized estimate of your health care cost after age 65.</p>
                    <div class="welcome-btn-wrapper">
                        <button class="btn btn-action-next btn-lg fs-5 shadow-sm fw-bold" onclick="appLogic.handleNext()">Start Setup</button>
                    </div>
                </section>
                
                <div class="shared-alignment">
                    
                    <section class="step-panel panel d-none">
                        <div class="question-block mb-4">
                            <h3 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-4">Q1. What is your current age?</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-4 fs-6">We'll take into consideration expected increases in health care costs between now and when you retire.</p>
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mt-4 pt-2 position-relative">
                                <input type="number" class="form-control custom-numeric-input fw-bold m-0" id="q1_age" name="q1_age" placeholder="55" min="18" max="100" style="width: 110px;" required>
                                <p class="custom-label-text m-0">years old</p>
                                <div class="invalid-feedback position-absolute" style="bottom: -25px;">Please enter a valid age (18-100).</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn-group-row d-flex gap-3 mt-5 pb-4">
                            <button class="btn btn-action-back fw-bold" onclick="appLogic.goBack()">Back</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-action-next fw-bold validation-next-btn" onclick="appLogic.handleNext()" disabled>Next</button>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="step-panel panel d-none">
                        <div class="question-block mb-4">
                            <h3 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-4">Q2. At what age do you expect to retire?</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-4 fs-6">This estimate begins at age 65, when most people become eligible for Medicare. Enter your age if you are already retired.</p>
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mt-4 pt-2 position-relative">
                                <input type="number" class="form-control custom-numeric-input fw-bold m-0" id="q2_retire_age" name="q2_retire_age" placeholder="65" min="50" max="100" style="width: 110px;" required>
                                <p class="custom-label-text m-0">years old</p>
                                <div class="invalid-feedback position-absolute" style="bottom: -25px;">Please enter a valid age (50-100).</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn-group-row d-flex gap-3 mt-5 pb-4">
                            <button class="btn btn-action-back fw-bold" onclick="appLogic.goBack()">Back</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-action-next fw-bold validation-next-btn" onclick="appLogic.handleNext()" disabled>Next</button>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="step-panel panel d-none">
                        <div class="question-block mb-5">
                            <h3 class="mb-4 fw-bold text-dark">Q3. What is your gender?</h3>
                            <div class="form-check form-check-inline me-4">
                                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q3_gender" id="genderMale" value="Male" required>
                                <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="genderMale">Male</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q3_gender" id="genderFemale" value="Female" required>
                                <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="genderFemale">Female</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="question-block mb-4">
                            <h3 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-4">Q4. What ZIP code do you live in the most of the year?</h3>
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mt-4 pt-2 position-relative">
                                <input type="text" pattern="\d{5}" class="form-control custom-numeric-input fw-bold m-0" id="q4_zip" name="q4_zip" placeholder="90210" minlength="5" maxlength="5" style="width: 140px;" required>
                                <p class="custom-label-text m-0">5 Digit zip code</p>
                                <div class="invalid-feedback position-absolute" style="bottom: -25px;">Please enter a valid 5-digit zip code.</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="btn-group-row d-flex gap-3 mt-5 pb-4">
                            <button class="btn btn-action-back fw-bold" onclick="appLogic.goBack()">Back</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-action-next fw-bold validation-next-btn" onclick="appLogic.handleNext()" disabled>Next</button>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="step-panel panel d-none">
                        <div class="question-block mb-4">
                            <h3 class="mb-4 fw-bold text-dark">Q5. Overall, compared to others your age, how would you describe your health?</h3>
                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-3 pt-2">
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q5_health" id="healthExc" value="Excellent" required>
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="healthExc">Excellent</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q5_health" id="healthVGood" value="Very Good">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="healthVGood">Very Good</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q5_health" id="healthGood" value="Good">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="healthGood">Good</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q5_health" id="healthFair" value="Fair">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="healthFair">Fair</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q5_health" id="healthPoor" value="Poor">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="healthPoor">Poor</label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn-group-row d-flex gap-3 mt-5 pb-4">
                            <button class="btn btn-action-back fw-bold" onclick="appLogic.goBack()">Back</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-action-next fw-bold validation-next-btn" onclick="appLogic.handleNext()" disabled>Next</button>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="step-panel panel d-none">
                        <h3 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-4">In the past 12 months</h3>
                        <div class="question-block mb-5">
                            <h3 class="mb-2 fw-bold text-dark">Q6. How many times have you visited your primary care doctor?</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-3 fs-6">Do not include routine or preventive visits, such as annual checkups.</p>
                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-3 pt-1">
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q6_primary_visits" id="pv0" value="0 visits" required>
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="pv0">0 visits</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q6_primary_visits" id="pv13" value="1-3 visits">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="pv13">1-3 visits</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q6_primary_visits" id="pv4" value="4 or more visits">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="pv4">4 or more visits</label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="question-block mb-4">
                            <h3 class="mb-3 fw-bold text-dark">Q7. How many times have you visited a specialist?</h3>
                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-3 pt-1">
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q7_spec_visits" id="sv0" value="0 visits" required>
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="sv0">0 visits</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q7_spec_visits" id="sv14" value="1-4 visits">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="sv14">1-4 visits</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q7_spec_visits" id="sv59" value="5-9 visits">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="sv59">5-9 visits</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q7_spec_visits" id="sv10" value="10 or more visits">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="sv10">10 or more visits</label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="btn-group-row d-flex gap-3 mt-5 pb-4">
                            <button class="btn btn-action-back fw-bold" onclick="appLogic.goBack()">Back</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-action-next fw-bold validation-next-btn" onclick="appLogic.handleNext()" disabled>Next</button>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="step-panel panel d-none">
                        <div class="question-block mb-4">
                            <h3 class="mb-4 fw-bold text-dark">Q8. How many times have you been admitted to the hospital in the past 12 months?</h3>
                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-3 pt-2">
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q8_hospital" id="hosp0" value="0 times" required>
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="hosp0">0 times</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q8_hospital" id="hosp1" value="1 time">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="hosp1">1 time</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q8_hospital" id="hosp2" value="2 or more times">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="hosp2">2 or more times</label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn-group-row d-flex gap-3 mt-5 pb-4">
                            <button class="btn btn-action-back fw-bold" onclick="appLogic.goBack()">Back</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-action-next fw-bold validation-next-btn" onclick="appLogic.handleNext()" disabled>Next</button>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="step-panel panel d-none">
                        <div class="question-block mb-5">
                            <h3 class="mb-4 fw-bold text-dark">Q9. What is your annual cost of prescription medication, before your insurance pays?</h3>
                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-3 pt-2">
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q9_rx_cost" id="rx1" value="under $250" required>
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="rx1">Under $250</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q9_rx_cost" id="rx2" value="$250 to $1,000">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="rx2">$250 to $1,000</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q9_rx_cost" id="rx3" value="$1,000 to $2,500">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="rx3">$1,000 to $2,500</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q9_rx_cost" id="rx4" value="2500 to 5000">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="rx4">$2,500 to $5,000</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q9_rx_cost" id="rx5" value="5000 or more">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="rx5">$5,000 or more</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q9_rx_cost" id="rx6" value="don't know">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="rx6">Don't know</label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="question-block mb-4">
                            <h3 class="mb-2 fw-bold text-dark">Q10. How many different prescription medications do you take on a regular basis?</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-3 fs-6">Do not include over-the-counter medications or prescriptions you don't take regularly.</p>
                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-3 pt-2">
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q10_rx_count" id="rxc0" value="0" required>
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="rxc0">0</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q10_rx_count" id="rxc1" value="1-2">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="rxc1">1-2</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q10_rx_count" id="rxc3" value="3-4">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="rxc3">3-4</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q10_rx_count" id="rxc5" value="5-6">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="rxc5">5-6</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q10_rx_count" id="rxc7" value="7 or more">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="rxc7">7 or more</label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="btn-group-row d-flex gap-3 mt-5 pb-4">
                            <button class="btn btn-action-back fw-bold" onclick="appLogic.goBack()">Back</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-action-next fw-bold validation-next-btn" onclick="appLogic.handleNext()" disabled>Next</button>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="step-panel panel d-none">
                        <div class="question-block mb-4">
                            <h3 class="mb-2 fw-bold text-dark">Q11. Do you have a family history of serious health conditions that could affect future medical costs?</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-3 fs-6">Examples include cancer, heart diseases, or neurological conditions.</p>
                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-3 pt-2">
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q11_history" id="histYes" value="Yes" required>
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="histYes">Yes</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q11_history" id="histNo" value="No">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="histNo">No</label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn-group-row d-flex gap-3 mt-5 pb-4">
                            <button class="btn btn-action-back fw-bold" onclick="appLogic.goBack()">Back</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-action-next fw-bold validation-next-btn" onclick="appLogic.handleNext()" disabled>Next</button>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                    <section class="step-panel panel d-none">
                        <div class="question-block mb-4">
                            <h3 class="mb-2 fw-bold text-dark">Q12. How many years of retirement would you like to plan for after age 65?</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-3 fs-6">For people similar to you, the average length of retirement after age 65 is about 20 years.</p>
                            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-3 pt-2">
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q12_retire_years" id="ry5" value="5 years" required>
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="ry5">5 years</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q12_retire_years" id="ry10" value="10 years">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="ry10">10 years</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q12_retire_years" id="ry15" value="15 years">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="ry15">15 years</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q12_retire_years" id="ry20" value="20 years">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="ry20">20 years</label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-check form-check-inline m-0">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="q12_retire_years" id="ry25" value="25+ years">
                                    <label class="form-check-label custom-radio-label" for="ry25">25+ years</label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="btn-group-row d-flex gap-3 mt-5 pb-4">
                            <button class="btn btn-action-back fw-bold" onclick="appLogic.goBack()">Back</button>
                            <button class="btn btn-action-next fw-bold text-nowrap validation-next-btn" style="width: auto !important; min-width: 220px !important; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px;" onclick="appLogic.handleNext()" disabled>Show me my Estimate</button>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                </div>
            </div>

            <section id="results-flow-container" class="step-panel panel d-none results-layout-canvas pt-5">
                <div class="results-page-inner">
                    <p class="fs-4 text-muted mb-4"><span class="fw-bold text-dark text-uppercase">lowest estimate cost:</span> <span class="fw-bold text-primary fs-3 ms-2" id="dynamic-cost-display">$3,200 / year</span></p>
                    
                    <div class="results-text-block mb-4">
                        <p class="fs-5 text-muted mb-3">Your personalized evaluation has compiled premium benchmarks adjusted against standard regional baseline parameters. This initial layout helps illustrate how strategic out-of-pocket variations distribute across your active coverage lifecycle.</p>
                        <p class="fs-5 text-muted mb-4">By balancing these anticipated premiums against active marketplace baseline tables, you can secure comprehensive supplemental protection parameters. Review the primary observations compiled below:</p>
                        <ul class="fs-5 text-muted ps-4" style="line-height: 1.8;">
                            <li>Out-of-pocket exposure tracks closely to local market utilization parameters.</li>
                            <li>Prescription expenditures present optimization opportunities via generic tier structural routing.</li>
                            <li>Annual supplemental premium adjustments stabilize significantly upon achieving threshold targets.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="results-table-image-grid mb-5 mt-5">
                        <div class="table-responsive">
                            <table class="table custom-result-table align-middle m-0 w-100">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th scope="col" style="width: 61.6%;">Coverage Component Category</th>
                                        <th scope="col" style="width: 38.4%;" class="text-end">Projected Base Annual Exposure</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr><td>Medicare Part B Premium Outlays</td><td class="text-end fw-bold text-dark">$2,040</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td>Supplemental Out-of-Pocket Insurance Layer</td><td class="text-end fw-bold text-dark">$1,150</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td>Prescription Formulary (Tier 1-3) Deductibles</td><td class="text-end fw-bold text-dark">$760</td></tr>
                                    <tr><td>Routine Clinical Ancillary Discretionary Fees</td><td class="text-end fw-bold text-dark">$300</td></tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1473186578172-c141e6798cf4?auto=format&fit=crop&w=400&h=420&q=80" class="results-bleed-img" alt="Retirement">
                    </div>

                    <div class="results-text-block mb-4">
                        <p class="fs-5 text-dark fw-bold mb-2">The table above presents a specialized analysis matching your reported health parameters against regional baseline models.</p>
                        <p class="fs-6 text-muted">Annual premium outlays scale incrementally based upon geographic adjustments and active insurance tier distribution criteria.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-5 mb-5 pt-3">
                        <button class="btn btn-action-next fw-bold shadow-sm" style="width: auto; padding: 0 32px;" onclick="appLogic.resetApp()">update my response</button>
                    </div>

